# SkyPANEL External Integrations

## VirtFusion API

The primary integration for server and user management:

- User synchronization with external relation ID mapping
- Server control (power, reset password, VNC access)
- Resource usage tracking for billing
- OS templates and package management

Key environment variables:
```
VIRTFUSION_API_URL=https://your-virtfusion.com/api/v1
VIRTFUSION_API_KEY=your_virtfusion_api_key
```

## Google Gemini AI

Integration for intelligent customer support:

- Context-aware response generation
- Support ticket assistance
- Discord bot integration

Key environment variables:
```
GOOGLE_AI_API_KEY=your_google_gemini_api_key
```

## Discord Integration

Two-way communication with Discord for support and notifications:

- Webhook notifications for tickets and system events
- Discord bot for ticket management and AI support
- User/role permission system

Key environment variables:
```
DISCORD_WEBHOOK_URL=https://discord.com/api/webhooks/your-webhook-url
DISCORD_BOT_TOKEN=your_discord_bot_token
DISCORD_GUILD_ID=your_discord_server_id
DISCORD_CHANNEL_ID=your_discord_channel_id
```

## PayPal Integration

Payment processing for credit purchases:

- Secure payment processing
- Webhook validation
- Transaction tracking

Key environment variables:
```
VITE_PAYPAL_SANDBOX=true_or_false
VITE_PAYPAL_CLIENT_ID=your_paypal_client_id
VITE_PAYPAL_SECRET=your_paypal_secret
VITE_PAYPAL_CURRENCY=USD
```

## BetterStack Monitoring

Real-time monitoring and status reporting:

- Service availability tracking
- Incident management
- Status page integration

Key environment variables:
```
BETTERSTACK_API_KEY=your_betterstack_api_key
```

## Email System (SMTP2GO)

Email delivery for notifications and verification:

- Account verification
- Password reset
- Transaction receipts
- Ticket notifications

Key environment variables:
```
SMTP2GO_API_KEY=your_smtp2go_api_key
SMTP_FROM=noreply@your-domain.com
SMTP_FROM_NAME=Your Company Support
```
